{"tid":942532,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人記得呢個mk仔 冇睇幾年老咗好多","createTime":"2018-12-15T19:03:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-16T04:04:06.000Z","uid":165817,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ee4f9444fd5ece3cb5f9780d643b10d4b39ccce8","tid":942532,"uid":165817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T19:03:47.000Z","msg":"天賦好高 技術好好<br />\n阿根廷喺美斯之前 出產好多好好技術嘅矮仔<br />\n奧迪加 加拿度 艾馬 個個都叫新馬勒當拿<br />\n另外一個就係佢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/w6kFN9H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fw6kFN9H.jpg&h=e2241cc7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MWoss9K.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMWoss9K.png&h=7c845b67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kESpvn3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkESpvn3.png&h=9a170bc2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當年個樣真係好串 一副壞孩子樣<br />\n踢波又挑釁 鍾意賣弄<br />\n紀律唔好又冇野心 一直都半紅不黑咁<br />\n最震撼應該係無啦啦走去樸茅護級<br />\n<br />\n原來佢十年已經返咗南美踢 一直踢到而家<br />\n冇睇咁耐 真係老咗好多<br />\n當年啲mk臭串銳氣都冇哂 好似穩重咗好多<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k5sT8aK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk5sT8aK.png&h=2ee8220c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3Rrd8aK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3Rrd8aK.png&h=faf52cd2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇人記得佢? 都算童年回憶"},{"pid":"dae25a56cfae2c39c556d31b2da7e6a6c20bd7f5","tid":942532,"uid":176283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T19:08:11.000Z","msg":"迪阿歷山度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9deb21f52f538d8a43a0ae310b20c698ed5f52f","tid":942532,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T19:34:25.000Z","msg":"當年吹到好大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"335a0fb6a23307a6995576fb5fe58cc3e81bcb9e","tid":942532,"uid":42626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-15T20:27:52.000Z","msg":"當年係winning 8識佢<br />\n佢最錯係去英超踢Portsmouth<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92f0842d969ca1cda64f011e38922a3017050d76","tid":942532,"uid":14075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-16T04:04:06.000Z","msg":"全盛時期係咪薩拉戈薩？"}]}